title: Spaceflight Idle Factory

container.value: Bures sur Yvette, 14 rue du docteur collé

creator: Kanapp3r
descriptionHtml:
In this Spaceflight exploration game, you will explore an craft your own base, and control a small settlement of astronauts ready to conquer space/new planets.

Build an assembly line with Conveyor belts, Factory, Foundry... and rebuild an industry capable of launching your spaceflight and rocket ships.

You will land on a new and undiscovered planet and will face many challenge :
-create your own assembly line with mining drills and factory and conveyor belts.
-Carefully engineer, optimize and automate your base with conveyor belts.
-Craft from scratch : ore -> bar -> screw/plate/electric wire -> CPU -> ... -> Spaceflight.
-Move your base with the help of thrusters, and search for new resources to mine and expend your base and production.
-Defend your base against this new wildlife.
descriptionShort: Build an assembly line with conveyor belts/factory and launch your rocketships

descriptionHtml:
In this Spaceflight simulation game, you will create your own base (defend it against swarms of enemies). Rebuild an assembly line to create spacecraft and explore the galaxy. with the help of a small settlement of astronauts ready to conquer space/new planets.

You can build an assembly line with Conveyor belts, Factory, Foundry... and rebuild an industry capable of launching your spacecrafts and rocket ships.

You will land on a new and undiscovered planet and will face many challenge :
-create your own assembly line with mining drills and factory and conveyor belts.
-Carefully engineer, optimize and automate your base with conveyor belts.
-Craft from scratch : ore -> bar -> screw/plate/electric wire -> CPU -> ... -> Spaceflight.
-Move your base with the help of thrusters, and search for new resources to mine and expend your base and production.
-Defend your base against this new wildlife.
descriptionShort: Build an assembly line with conveyor belts/factory and launch your spacecrafts
